line_1: With aching Head, and squeamish Heart-Burnings;
line_2: Yet lov'd in Secret all forbidden Things.

line_1: With aching Head, and squeamish Heart-Burnings;
line_2: And here the Tertian shakes his chilling Wings;

line_1: With aching Head, and squeamish Heart-Burnings;
line_2: A Wolf now gnaws him, now a Serpent stings;
